Class Reader

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.jwang73.stars.Reader

  • public class Reader
extends Object
    This class is primarily responsible for taking in a csv path and processing its data, and an intermediary layer between Main and KDTree to simplify Main's run method.
